{
  "stem": "23278.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I felt my children should be raised in America.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But how?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had the life insurance.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I could live maybe five years.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And after that, what do I do?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My little boy was only three.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I decided since I had a masters degree, I would become a teacher.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I came back here in the summer, and I went to Teacher's College.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I learned what it is to be an idiot at Teacher's College-- oh, my.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I mean, to think that they formed teachers there, that was shameful.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Anyway, I wrote such good paper that they sent me to the main university to get a Ph.D.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So in that, they were good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I told my parents, I have an occasion to do a Ph.D.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That's going to take much of my money, but can I leave the children with you?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they said, all right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So I left the children in France with my father and my mother for three years, except that I spend six months of each year for the summer vacation with them.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I took all my classes, everything, in 18 months [LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I took my German, my Latin exam, boom, boom, boom, quick.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, I had a good French education.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That helped me a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I landed my first job at Bonn University, where I finished my dissertation.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When I had my job, I had my children come back to me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was there in competition with men who had nothing to do than to get home and put their feet under the table and eat dinner and do their research, where I had to care for family, to earn a living, having no maid, no help, no washing machine, taking care of the homework.",
      "word_count": 55
    }
  ],
